'''Map reader''' was a generic term for any device that projected [[Hologram/Legends|holograms]] of maps. The [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] used map readers in the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]] to display [[Star Map|star maps]].

[[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], the [[Bear Clan]], and [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] used a map reader when discussing the disappearance of [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]] from the [[Jedi Archives/Legends|Jedi Archives]].

